name: Geek Tree 03 : Pac-man death
description:
In the last century, somewhere in 1980, technology, Man, was limited to Pac Pac Pac.
At the end of 2022, after a 3rd World War which lasted 3 days, there are only 2 PCs left, which reminds all of humanity. While they were doomed to their sad fate, a flash worthy of "back to the future" briefly brought them back to life. Yeah.. All for... that! (and in addition there is a bug)
